events.name: Open Tech, Big Data and Summer of Code with FOSSASIA
events.description:
We are meeting to learn more about the current coding at FOSSASIA, scholarships and internship opportunities with Google Summer of Code. We are planning a presentation about Big Data with loklak and participants have the chance for shoutouts. After the presentations you are welcome to ask questions to mentors, students, participants in the FOSSASIA community. If you are interested in open technologies please join us! 


Agenda • Introduction and updates after Code-In gatherings in San Francisco and Shanghai • Latest releases of current software projects and activities of FOSSASIA • Presentation on internships with Google Summer of Code and FOSSASIA in the field of Big Data • Q&A and Networking 


Links Twitter: http://twitter.com/fossasia Website: http://fossasia.org
